---
<BlogLayout
  title="Japanese Keigo: A Complete Guide to Polite Language"
  description="Master Japanese keigo (honorific language) — learn the three types (teineigo, sonkeigo, kenjougo), daily keigo phrases, the uchi-soto principle, and common mistakes to avoid."
