    <p style="margin: 8px 0 0;">Do not try to memorize all keigo at once. Start with teineigo (which you likely already know), then learn the 10 most common sonkeigo/kenjougo verb pairs. Focus on recognition first — being able to understand keigo when you hear it — before worrying about perfect production. Practice daily phrases with our <a href="/japanese/tools/daily-phrase/">Daily Phrase tool</a> and build vocabulary with the <a href="/japanese/tools/jlpt-vocabulary/">JLPT Vocabulary tool</a>.</p>
